description: Factor level shows annual FYM treatment

Factor level shows annual FYM treatment. Applied in autumn usually to stubble of previous crop. Applied to strip 22 since 1843, to strip 21 since 1885 and to strip 1 1968-2000. No FYM applied to oats, 1996-2017. No FYM applied to beans 2018-
Factor level shows annual FYM treatment. Indicates that FYM was applied, 1968-2000. Strip 1.
